sec.p:
For modelling purposes, the DH demand in EnergyPLAN was divided into three groups:
DH1: DH demand in DH systems with heat-only boilers (HOB);
DH2: DH demand in DH systems with heat-only boilers and back-pressure CHP plants, which cannot operate without a heat demand;
DH3: DH demand in DH systems with heat-only boilers and CHP plants which can operate in condensing mode, i.e. produce only electricity.
